# IP Addressing & VLAN Plan

This file documents the full IP addressing scheme, VLAN allocation, and authentication setup for the **HQ–Branch Secure Network Lab**.

---

## HQ Campus

### ASA-HQ Interfaces
| Interface        | Nameif       | Security Level | IP Address        | Description           |
|------------------|-------------|----------------|-------------------|------------------------|
| Gi1/1            | outside     | 0              | 203.0.113.1/30    | Uplink to ISP-HQ       |
| Gi1/2            | inside-MS1  | 100            | 10.1.1.2/30       | Link to MS1-HQ Core    |
| Gi1/3            | inside-MS2  | 100            | 10.1.1.6/30       | Link to MS2-HQ Core    |
| Gi1/4            | DMZ         | 70             | 192.168.10.1/24   | DMZ Segment            |

---

### HQ VLANs
| VLAN | Name        | Subnet              | HSRP Virtual IP | MS1 IP      | MS2 IP      | Notes              |
|------|------------|---------------------|-----------------|-------------|-------------|--------------------|
| 20   | Engineers  | 192.168.20.0/24     | 192.168.20.1    | .2          | .3          | DHCP Relay to DMZ  |
| 30   | Office     | 192.168.30.0/24     | 192.168.30.1    | .2          | .3          | DHCP Relay to DMZ  |
| 40   | Sales      | 192.168.40.0/24     | 192.168.40.1    | .2          | .3          | DHCP Relay to DMZ  |
| 50   | IT         | 192.168.50.0/24     | 192.168.50.1    | .2          | .3          | DHCP Relay to DMZ  |
| 60   | Mgmt       | 192.168.60.0/24     | 192.168.60.1    | .2          | .3          | Static IPs only, SSH access allowed |

---

### HQ Servers (DMZ)
| Server      | IP Address     | Services            |
|-------------|----------------|---------------------|
| DNS Server  | 192.168.10.3   | DNS                 |
| DHCP Server | 192.168.10.4   | DHCP for HQ VLANs   |
| DHCP Server | 192.168.10.5   | DHCP for BranchVLAN |
| Web Server  | 192.168.10.6   | HTTP/HTTPS          |
| Email       | 192.168.10.7   | SMTP/IMAP           |
| FTP/NTP     | 192.168.10.8   | FTP, NTP            |

---

## Branch Campus

### ASA-Branch Interfaces
| Interface        | Nameif       | Security Level | IP Address        | Description            |
|------------------|-------------|----------------|-------------------|------------------------|
| Gi1/1            | outside     | 0              | 203.0.113.5/30    | Uplink to ISP-Branch   |
| Gi1/2            | inside-MS1  | 100            | 10.1.2.2/30       | Link to MS1-Branch     |
| Gi1/3            | inside-MS2  | 100            | 10.1.2.6/30       | Link to MS2-Branch     |

---

### Branch VLANs
| VLAN | Name        | Subnet              | HSRP Virtual IP | MS1 IP      | MS2 IP      | Notes               |
|------|------------|---------------------|-----------------|-------------|-------------|---------------------|
| 70   | Marketing  | 172.16.70.0/24      | 172.16.70.1     | .2          | .3          | DHCP Relay to DHCP-BR |
| 80   | Office     | 172.16.80.0/24      | 172.16.80.1     | .2          | .3          | DHCP Relay to DHCP-BR |
| 90   | Sales      | 172.16.90.0/24      | 172.16.90.1     | .2          | .3          | DHCP Relay to DHCP-BR |
| 60   | Mgmt       | 172.16.60.0/24      | 172.16.60.1     | .2          | .3          | Static IPs only, SSH access allowed |

---

## WAN / ISP / Internet

| Device     | Interface        | IP Address       | Notes                          |
|------------|-----------------|------------------|--------------------------------|
| Internet   | S0/1/0 → ISP-HQ | 10.10.10.2/30    | Toward ASA-HQ ISP              |
| Internet   | S0/1/1 → ISP-BR | 20.20.20.2/30    | Toward ASA-Branch ISP          |
| ISP-HQ     | G0/0/0          | 203.0.113.2/30   | Facing ASA-HQ outside          |
| ISP-Branch | G0/0/0          | 203.0.113.6/30   | Facing ASA-Branch outside      |

---

## Authentication

- **All passwords**: `cisco`  
- Applies to:
  - Console (`line con 0`)  
  - VTY (`line vty 0 4`)  
  - Enable secret  
  - SSH login  

Only **VLAN60 (Management)** is allowed to initiate SSH sessions.


